    {
      "id": "67227c8d-69b3-42bc-9dfa-00d6d6747f54",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors used eye-tracking to rpedict learning performance. Results show that the combination of eye-tracking with other behavior attributes may be useful for accurate predictions of learning performance. ",
